Introduction

Kang Hyunwoo is a South Korean trainee under Eighty6.

On May 20, 2021, he was introduced as a contestant on SBS' survival show LOUD but was eliminated in the sixth round.

On February 20, 2023, Kang Hyunwoo was revealed as a contestant on MBC's survival show Fantasy Boys. He was sadly eliminated in episode 10 and wasn't able to debut in the final group.

He was introduced as a member of the upcoming Japanese boy group MY BOYZ on October 2, 2023. However, no news about the group have been shared in 2024.

On September 26, 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7, which started in October 2024. He was eliminated in the final after ranking 10th place.
